    "summary": "The transcript depicts a user expressing profound grief and suicidal ideation following the loss of a pet, describing a desire to \"not exist\" to find peace. The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's emotional pain while consistently redirecting them toward professional crisis support and help resources.",
